premise_source_doc_sentence: Sean Patrick Flanery  (  born October 11 , 1965  )  is an American actor , author , and martial artist , known for playing Connor MacManus in The Boondock Saints , Greg Stillson in The Dead Zone , Jeremy `` Powder '' Reed in Powder , Indiana Jones in The Young Indiana Jones Chronicles , as well as Bobby Dagen in Saw : The Final Chapter .
